      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new ebook called \"The Global Professional\" and i want to include a chapter on what it actually means to be \"sophisticated\" and \"proper\" in high-end international business circles. can u give me a breakdown of the core standards for professional etiquette and sophisticated behavior that someone should follow to be taken seriously globally?",
