      "content": "i see, so basically a very Western European/American corporate approach. i want to make sure the book doesn't just sound like a manual for London or NYC. how would you categorize the difference between that \"gold standard\" you mentioned and, say, how someone from a place like India, Nigeria, or Japan might approach professionalism? i want to show how those styles differ from the standard.",
